title: Best Daytona scanner sound: 'You can't be that stupid!' | FOX Sports
text:
Feb 22, 2017 at 9:16a ET 0Shares 
With no points on the line, calamity was expected in a rain-delayed daytime version of the Advance Auto Parts Clash. 
From Jimmie Johnson getting loose and clipping Kurt Busch, sending him into the wall to Denny Hamlinâ€™s block on Brad Keselowski, the Clash lived up to the hype. 
Joey Logano grabbed the first victory of the season and left Kyle Busch a bit peeved at Alex Bowman for not teaming up to chase down the No. 22 Ford as the two battled to the line. 
Check out the best scanner sound from Daytona on the first edition of Radioactive in 2017.
